data.description: This Grasonville Home had to temporarily come off the market due to some family matters dont miss your opportunity to own a little piece of heaven, this beautiful home sits  on a Corner Lot w/ over 2000 sq ft. Property is priced to sell! features custom kitchen w/ 6' island, large rear deck, main lvl 1/2 bath, spa like master bath, walk-in closet, large bedrooms, great natural lighting, garage, shed, vinyl fencing, flat functional yard, recessed lighting, vaulted ceilings, crown molding, surround sound & more! Quiet Community with private road close to the elementary school and local parks, fishing ponds, as well as Pin Tail Point for the skeet and trap shooting enthusiast!
